entries.arrival_phase_1: Scanning system for target. Stand by to proceed with the attack.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Nav location to the target has been located. Proceed with extreme prejudice.
entries.assassinate_success: Good work, pilot. We should be pinpointing the location of the second Ragtag squad shortly.
entries.destroy_escort: The entire squad must be eradicated.
entries.failed_escape: You let them escape! Return to Demmi Wot for further instructions.
entries.quest_escort_t: Destroy the Rest of the Squad
entries.quest_location_d: The squad of Ragtag fighters is known to patrol parts of the Corellia System.
entries.quest_target_d: Take out the Squad Leader of the band of Ragtag fighters.
entries.title: Corellia System: Destroy the First Squad of Ragtags
entries.title_d: Some Ragtags have been vandalizing the Coronet starport. Destroy the first of the two squads in order to put a stop to their vandalism.
